---
title: Sticky Honey and Sambal Aubergine Stir-Fry with Jasmine Rice and Peanut & Coriander Dressing
description: Our Sticky Honey and Sambal Aubergine Stir-Fry is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R20_W30_UK_QR14906-3_Main__3low-a5018ef1.jpg
